Lego Release 1.3.1      November 1998
=====================================


README
  This file

Makefile
lego.sh
  Makefile to install lego, and skeleton shell script to run it.
  Instructions below.

lib
  Lego library (including sources)

src
  SML source for Lego  (For SML NJ 0.93)


To install lego:
================

 Edit the Makefile if necessary, then run 'make install'

 Defaults:

   /usr/local/lib/lego    Lego library and binaries
   /usr/local/bin/lego    } Scripts to invoke Lego, possibly
   /usr/local/bin/legoML  } setting LEGOPATH.


More information and documentation of new features:
===================================================

 See	    http://www.dcs.ed.ac.uk/~lego

 Email to:  lego@dcs.ed.ac.uk

